metadata.name: Chief Toad #1
metadata.description:
Chief Toad is a collection of 10,000 unique Chief Toad NFTs. Your Chief Toad NFT doubles as G-Link's membership which gives VIP access to G-Link's gameverse platform.

  Perks include the ability to create guilds in the gameverse, enjoy higher in-game earnings, acquire early access to games in beta and virtual land sales, and receive benefits during the GLINK token initial decentralized exchange offering (IDO).
